found in  409.32. (Also see  409.33 (a) and (b) for a description of examples of skilled nursing and rehabilitation
services.) 

(2) Physical therapy services that meet the requirements of  409.44(b). 

(3) Speech-language pathology services that meet the requirements of  409.44(b). 







