III. Analysis of Comments



A. Comments to the Proposed Rule




Comments regarding the October 6, 1993, Notice of Proposed Rulemaking (NPRM) were received from 264 entities. Over
half (157) were submitted by businesses; 33 by educational facilities; 23 by attorneys; and 21 by the general public.
The rest of the commenters were distributed among members of Congress (3), the AFL-CIO (1), the Embassy of India
(1), Federal Government employees (5), State governments (6), and trade associations (15).



